{"title":"2020-10-06","virtualPath":"/Diary/","anchorUrl":"/Gitwee/timeline/2020/10/06#MT9gpkaEUm","html":"<div class=\"markdown-body\"><p>walking の前にメガシンカしておいた。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-194323-Screenshot_20201005-194323.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-194323-Screenshot_20201005-194323.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>こいつがやってきた。何かに使えんの？</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-205734-Screenshot_20201005-205734.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-205734-Screenshot_20201005-205734.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>そしてとうとう…</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-213743-Screenshot_20201005-213743.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-213743-Screenshot_20201005-213743.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>おっさんに。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-213843-Screenshot_20201005-213843.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-213843-Screenshot_20201005-213843.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>すげー不細工。笑うな笑うな。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-214841-Screenshot_20201005-214841.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-214841-Screenshot_20201005-214841.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a>\n<a href=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-235245-Screenshot_20201005-235245.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-235245-Screenshot_20201005-235245.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n<p>2700km かー。なかなか感慨ぶかい。</p>\n<p><a href=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-215446-Screenshot_20201005-215446.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"img/2020/2020-10-05/20201005-215446-Screenshot_20201005-215446.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:100%;\"></a></p>\n</div>","styles":["/css/github-markdown.css","/css/markdown-include.css"],"description":"日記,つぶやき,雑記帳","updated":"2020-10-06T13:48:58","published":"2020-10-06T13:48:58"}